ne" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1097_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1098_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1100_">You can easily create a customer account by clicking on the “Log-in” found in the navigation bar. By this, you’ll be able to save your cart and sign-in to view your order whenever you want.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1101_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1102_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="cb42416a-69f4-449b-99a9-d42c3469e8dd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I retrieve my password?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="cb42416a-69f4-449b-99a9-d42c3469e8dd" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1104_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1105_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1107_">Please use the "Forgot my password" option located on the login page on our website. It will walk you through resetting passwords.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-gjNHFA hBngIv pf-1108_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1109_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1110_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1111_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1113_">The Emma Original Mattress</span></h4><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1114_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1116_">About the Emma Original Mattress</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1117_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1118_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1119_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c8e1a6b7-cf21-4124-9c80-db4645d27423" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What makes the Emma Original Mattress special?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c8e1a6b7-cf21-4124-9c80-db4645d27423" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1121_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1122_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1124_">The Emma Original, with over 75 product awards, is composed of three layers. Its AIRGOCELL® foam technology dissipates sweat and absorbs heat so that you sleep cool and comfortable. Its HALO® Memory Foam has 3 zones that adapt to your body shape and has motion isolation technology so that you get better pressure relief and uninterrupted sleep. Its HRX® Supreme Foam has 5 adaptive cutouts that distribute your body weight evenly so that you get full body support.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1125_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1126_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="249c80db-4645-4274-a307-e36e75e67b4a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How is the Emma Original Mattress constructed?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="249c80db-4645-4274-a307-e36e75e67b4a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1128_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1129_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1131_">The Emma Original Mattress consists of 5 different layers:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1132_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1133_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1134_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1135_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1137_">The Plush Emma UltraDry® Original Cover with its temperature-regulating technology allows for a breathable cover and makes mattress maintenance easy.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1138_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1140_">The AIRGOCELL® foam has an open-pore cell structure and enables pleasant air circulation while keeping you cool, even on warm nights</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1141_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1143_">Motion-isolating HALO® Memory foam uses 3-zone support to balance out pressure points that will help you get a better night's sleep.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1144_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1146_">The Emma HRX Supreme® Foam is engineered to last for years and serves as the foundational support of the mattress.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1147_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1149_">Emma Edge Support provides a reinforced perimeter that not only helps prevent restless and active sleepers from falling off at night but also helps all sleepers easily sit up in the morning.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1150_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1151_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="443c633f-9419-4df9-a9a8-6deac9b4a258" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What certifications does the Emma Original Mattress have?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="443c633f-9419-4df9-a9a8-6deac9b4a258" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1153_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1154_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1156_">The foam used to make the Emma Original mattress is CertiPUR-US® and Class I (16.0.93305) of STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1157_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1158_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="f969a86d-eac9-44a2-98ca-6ff86befef7a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the sizes available for the Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="f969a86d-eac9-44a2-98ca-6ff86befef7a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1160_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1161_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1163_">Our Emma Original Mattress comes in 6 sizes– find one that suits you!</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1164_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1165_"><ul style="--text-indent:0px;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1166_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1167_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1169_">Twin: 38” x 75” x 10’’ (35 lbs) - Best for children, teens, or anyone under six feet tall.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1170_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1172_">Twin XL: 38” x 80” x 10’’ (37 lbs) - Best for growing children and/or teens.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1173_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1175_">Full: 54” x 75” x 10’’ (48 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples looking for something compact yet&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1176_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1178_">Queen: 60” x 80” x 10’’ (58 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples who want extra space.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1179_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1181_">King: 76” x 80” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for families who sleep together.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1182_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1184_">California King: 72” x 84” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for maximized space and comfort for your family and even pets.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1185_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1186_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1187_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1189_">If you’re still undecided on what size to get, we’d be more than willing to help you out. You may reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1190_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1191_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1192_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1193_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1195_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1196_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1198_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1199_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1201_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1202_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1203_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="8f75e696-cce5-445c-a54c-dfea51b94f8d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Original Mattress fit on any bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="8f75e696-cce5-445c-a54c-dfea51b94f8d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1205_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1206_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1208_">Yes, the Emma Original Mattress will fit in the majority of the appropriate bed frames.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1209_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1210_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="5c654cdf-ea51-494f-8d54-f46ec1bd2e80" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Original Mattress fire retardant?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5c654cdf-ea51-494f-8d54-f46ec1bd2e80" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1212_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1213_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1215_">Yes, the Emma Original mattress is compliant with the Canadian fire safety regulations and does not use chemicals to meet this requirement.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1216_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1217_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="4f8d54f4-6ec1-4d2e-80fc-427402c6274d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does it need a topper or bed cover?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4f8d54f4-6ec1-4d2e-80fc-427402c6274d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1219_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1220_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1222_">You do not need a topper or a bed cover to use the Emma Original Mattress. However, if you would like to control the softness/firmness of your mattress, our Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper will help you achieve just that. For more information, you may view our Topper <a href="/products/emma-topper" target="_blank">here.
</a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1223_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1224_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1225_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1227_">Is the Emma Original Mattress right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1228_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1229_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1230_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c6274d2c-a929-4631-9b80-b57e1b4a41c4" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the foam smell?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c6274d2c-a929-4631-9b80-b57e1b4a41c4" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1232_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1233_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1235_">Like all new products, the Emma Original mattress has a slight "new" smell at the start which will wear out over time. However, rest assured, the foams in our Emma Original have passed both CertiPUR-US® &amp; OEKO-TEX® certifications, which mean that those smells are temporary and harmless as we are free of harmful chemicals such as formaldehyde, phthalates, and flame retardants, as verified by an independent third-party organization.
<br><br>&nbsp;However, if the odor is bothering you, allow your mattress to air out for 24 hours, at which point the odor should subside. Should you have any more concerns, please reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1236_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1237_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1238_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1239_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1241_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1242_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1244_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1245_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1247_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1248_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1249_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="21a728db-2edd-4446-862b-fec0fb27390b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How firm is the Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="21a728db-2edd-4446-862b-fec0fb27390b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1251_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1252_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1254_">The Emma Original Mattress is considered ‘Medium Firm’. To help you out, imagine sleeping in cloudy comfort where we’re soft enough to feel comfortable and cozy while having that firmness to support your body as if someone was cuddling you to sleep.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1255_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1256_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="46862bfe-c0fb-4739-8ba1-b91b5c199eff" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Original Mattress vegan?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="46862bfe-c0fb-4739-8ba1-b91b5c199eff" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1258_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1259_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1261_">The foam used to make the Emma Original mattress is CertiPUR-US® and Class I (16.0.93305) of STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®.Yes, the Emma Original Mattress is 100 % vegan and does not contain any animal-based materials. Unfortunately, the mattress is inedible.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1262_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1263_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="390ba1b9-1b5c-499e-bf0f-1f99ba75b061" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>I have back or neck pain, is Emma Original Mattress the right mattress for me?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="390ba1b9-1b5c-499e-bf0f-1f99ba75b061" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1265_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1266_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1268_">We understand that needs vary by individuals so we offer 365 days to test the Emma Original mattress risk-free. That way you can decide if it is best for your situation.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1269_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1270_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1271_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1273_">How do I take care of my Emma Original Mattress?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1274_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1275_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1276_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="75b06199-a53c-4230-874f-58a20173b5e6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash my Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="75b06199-a53c-4230-874f-58a20173b5e6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1278_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1279_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1281_">Yes, but you may only wash the Plush Emma UltraDry® Original Cover of your mattress. Just open the zip and separate the top from the bottom part. For specific information, you may see their individual wash-label details.</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1282_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1283_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-1284_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058_1200x.png?v=1658749112" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058.png?v=1658749112 1536w" width="637" height="189" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1285_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1286_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="58a20173-b5e6-4c2f-825f-02cfe4ea91da" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the mattress considered a medical device?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="58a20173-b5e6-4c2f-825f-02cfe4ea91da" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1288_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1289_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1291_">No, the Emma Original mattress is not a medical device.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1292_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1293_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2f025f02-cfe4-4a91-9a21-06e5366be010" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long can my Emma mattress stay in the box for?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2f025f02-cfe4-4a91-9a21-06e5366be010" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1295_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1296_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1298_">The Emma Original mattress shouldn't be left rolled up in the box for more than four weeks after delivery as this may damage your mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1299_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1300_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="91da2106-e536-4be0-907e-9f0e70e139b8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do I need to flip and ventilate it?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="91da2106-e536-4be0-907e-9f0e70e139b8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1302_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1303_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1305_">No. Flipping your Emma Original mattress is not necessary and the white top-cover and AIRGOCELL® layer should always remain on top. The three layers of foam serve as an especially long-lived function of support, so the usual flipping of the mattress isn’t necessary. The special breathability and open-cell character of the core materials provide a self-contained ventilation system, keeping the mattress aerated.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1306_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1307_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1308_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1310_">Returns &amp; Delivery</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1311_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1312_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1313_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e139b8f0-7fd0-4839-a87d-fc314c0511d6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I return my Emma Original Mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e139b8f0-7fd0-4839-a87d-fc314c0511d6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1315_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1316_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1318_">You may return your Emma Original Mattress within 365 nights of receiving your product. When you want to return your Emma Original Mattress, please contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1319_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1320_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1321_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1322_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1324_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1325_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1327_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1328_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1330_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1331_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1332_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="61338786-79d4-4a7d-80d4-4787ea33e036" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Original Mattress have a warranty?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="61338786-79d4-4a7d-80d4-4787ea33e036" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1334_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1335_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1337_">The Emma Original Mattress has a 10-year-warranty upon receipt. For more information on warranty claims, please visit our <a href="/pages/terms-and-conditions" target="_blank">Terms and Conditions</a> or contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1338_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1339_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1340_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1341_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1343_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1344_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1346_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1347_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1349_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-gjNHFA hBngIv pf-1350_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1351_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1352_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1353_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1355_">The Emma Original Mattress</span></h4><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1356_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1358_">About the Emma Climax® Hybrid</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1359_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1360_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1361_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="f1d7e707-c144-499c-a0aa-57cc5797aaa3" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What Makes the Emma Climax® Hybrid special?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="f1d7e707-c144-499c-a0aa-57cc5797aaa3" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1363_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1364_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1366_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid is composed of six layers designed for heavy sleepers and couples alike. It showcases our new Climax® Pocketed Springs, which are individually wrapped coils engineered for the optimum tension and bounce to provide strong enough support for all types of sleepers and activities in bed. Aside from the pocketed springs, it has the award-winning AIRGOCELL® foam technology that dissipates sweat and absorbs heat so that nights are only hot (and steamy) when you want them to.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1367_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1368_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9ca0aa57-cc57-47aa-a3cf-8ac874eb50af" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How is the Emma Climax® Hybrid constructed?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9ca0aa57-cc57-47aa-a3cf-8ac874eb50af" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1370_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1371_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1373_">The Emma Climax Hybrid®  consists of 6 different layers:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1374_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1375_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1376_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1377_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1379_">The UltraDry® Pillowtop Cover has climate-regulating and moisture-wicking technology that allows for a breathable cover and makes mattress maintenance easy.
</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1380_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1382_">The AIRGOCELL® Hypersoft Comfort Layer has an open-pore cell structure and enables air circulation and dissipates body heat so nights only get hot (and steamy) when you want them to.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1383_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1385_">The Climax® Transition Layer is an adaptive memory foam with over 100 supportive points and 5 zoned cutouts that adapts to your body to provide optimal spinal alignment and pressure relief</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1386_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1388_">The Climax® Pocketed Springs are individually wrapped pocketed coils designed for the optimum tension and bounce to provide strong enough support for all types of sleepers. It also enhances airflow for better breathability and a cool night’s sleep.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1389_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1391_">The HRX Supreme® Edge Support provides a reinforced perimeter that not only helps prevent restless and active sleepers from falling off at night but also helps all sleepers easily sit up in the morning.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1392_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1394_">The HRX Supreme® Support Layer is a base foam layer that is guaranteed to provide support and withstand decades of use by heavy sleepers and couples alike.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1395_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1396_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="45ed2fb7-156e-412e-abaf-18a9991b36d8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What certifications does the Emma Climax® Hybrid have?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="45ed2fb7-156e-412e-abaf-18a9991b36d8" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1398_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1399_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1401_">The foam used to make the Emma Original mattress is CertiPUR-US® certified.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1402_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1403_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2eabaf18-a999-4b36-98e6-e44685e28be2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the sizes available?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2eabaf18-a999-4b36-98e6-e44685e28be2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1405_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1406_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1408_">Our Emma Climax® Hybrid comes in 6 sizes– find one that suits you!&nbsp;</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1409_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1410_"><ul style="--text-indent:0px;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1411_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1412_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1414_">Twin: 38” x 75” x 10’’ (35 lbs) - Best for children, teens, or anyone under six feet tall.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1415_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1417_">Twin XL: 38” x 80” x 10’’ (37 lbs) - Best for growing children and/or teens.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1418_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1420_">Full: 54” x 75” x 10’’ (48 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples looking for something compact yet&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1421_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1423_">Queen: 60” x 80” x 10’’ (58 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples who want extra space.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1424_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1426_">King: 76” x 80” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for families who sleep together.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1427_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1429_">California King: 72” x 84” x 10’’ (72 lbs) - Best for maximized space and comfort for your family and even pets.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1430_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1431_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1432_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1434_">If you’re still undecided on what size to get, we’d be more than willing to help you out. You may reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1435_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1436_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1437_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1438_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1440_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1441_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1443_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1444_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1446_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1447_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1448_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d93dc7f2-3443-4a88-862a-d0781dced0cb" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Climax® Hybrid fit on any bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d93dc7f2-3443-4a88-862a-d0781dced0cb" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1450_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1451_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1453_">Yes, the Emma Climax® Hybrid will fit in the majority of the appropriate bed frames.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1454_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1455_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="88862ad0-781d-4ed0-8b6b-3bb6772e2b40" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Climax® Hybrid fire retardant?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="88862ad0-781d-4ed0-8b6b-3bb6772e2b40" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1457_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1458_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1460_">Yes! The Emma Climax® Hybrid is constructed to comply with applicable safety laws and is fire retardant. We make sure to keep your safety in mind when engineering our products.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1461_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1462_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d0cb6b3b-b677-4e2b-8014-79d717d8537e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Climax® Hybrid need a topper or bed cover?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d0cb6b3b-b677-4e2b-8014-79d717d8537e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1464_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1465_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1467_">You do not need a topper or a bed cover for the Emma Climax® Hybrid. The use of a topper might affect the bounciness of the mattress. However, if you would like to control the softness/firmness of your mattress, our Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper will help you achieve just that. For more information, you may view our Topper&nbsp;<a href="/products/emma-topper" target="_blank">here.
</a></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1468_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1469_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="04e031ee-0d84-46c8-8de9-ac46624125d9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What’s the difference between the Emma Original Mattress and the Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="04e031ee-0d84-46c8-8de9-ac46624125d9" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1471_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1472_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1474_">The award-winning Emma Original Mattress is recommended for all sleepers, regardless of your sleeping position. Made with the breathable AIRGOCELL® and HRX Supreme base layer, the Emma Original distributes body weight evenly, relieves pressure and eliminates motion transfer for your best night’s sleep.
<br><br>The Emma Climax® Hybrid is recommended for sleepers who want extra support, and for those who want to do more than sleep. It combines the award-winning comfort, zero motion transfer, zoned support and pressure relief of our Emma Original with the breathability, bounce and extra support of our  Climax® Pocketed Springs. 

Both Emma mattresses are considered medium-firm, offering the perfect mix of comfort and support.
</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1475_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1476_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1477_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1479_">Is the Emma Climax® Hybrid right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1480_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1481_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1482_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d8537e4b-ecc6-4afa-b33c-7846bd1b152a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the foam smell?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d8537e4b-ecc6-4afa-b33c-7846bd1b152a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1484_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1485_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1487_">Like all new products, the Emma Climax® Hybrid has a slight "new" smell at the start which will wear out over time. However, rest assured, the foams in our mattress have passed both CertiPUR-US® &amp; OEKO-TEX® certification. This means that those smells are temporary and harmless, as the foams are free of harmful chemicals such as formaldehyde, phthalates, and flame retardants, as verified by an independent third-party organization.
<br><br>&nbsp;However, if the odor is bothering you, allow your mattress to air out for 24 hours, at which point the odor should subside. Should you have any more concerns, please reach out to our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1488_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1489_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1490_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1491_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1493_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1494_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1496_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1497_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1499_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1500_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1501_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="5b958434-fbf2-4a46-a16d-698dc62de478" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How firm is the Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5b958434-fbf2-4a46-a16d-698dc62de478" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1503_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1504_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1506_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid is considered to be ‘Medium Firm’, a 6 on a 1-10 scale, 1 being the softest. To help you out, imagine sleeping in cloudy comfort where we’re soft enough to feel comfortable and cozy while having that firmness to support your body as if someone was cuddling you to sleep.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1507_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1508_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="46616d69-8dc6-4de4-b83c-510e43e205e2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Climax® Hybrid vegan?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="46616d69-8dc6-4de4-b83c-510e43e205e2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1510_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1511_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1513_">Yes, the Emma Original Mattress is 100 % vegan and does not contain any animal-based materials.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1514_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1515_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e4783c51-0e43-4205-a2b2-5effadcbace2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>I have back or neck pain, is the Emma Climax® Hybrid the right mattress for me?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e4783c51-0e43-4205-a2b2-5effadcbace2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1517_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1518_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1520_">The Climax® Hybrid is constructed with the Climax® Transition Layer with over 100 supportive points and 5 zoned cutouts that contours and adapts to your body for optimal spinal alignment and pressure relief.  We understand that needs vary by individuals so we offer 365 days to test the Emma Climax® Hybrid risk-free. That way you can decide if it is best for your situation.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1521_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1522_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1523_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1525_">How do I take care of my Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1526_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1527_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1528_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="cbace2f5-6e4a-4664-89c2-9c8bbecbf287" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash my Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="cbace2f5-6e4a-4664-89c2-9c8bbecbf287" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1530_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1531_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1533_">Yes, but you may only wash the Plush Emma UltraDry® Original Cover of your mattress. Just open the zip and separate the top from the bottom part. For specific information, you may see their individual wash-label details.</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1534_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1535_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jObWnj dWwBay pf-1536_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058_1200x.png?v=1658749112" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/t/22/assets/wash-labels-1658749111058.png?v=1658749112 1536w" width="637" height="189" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy"/></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1537_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1538_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9c8bbecb-f287-4dd5-b1d9-43fade6aac0c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the mattress considered a medical device?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9c8bbecb-f287-4dd5-b1d9-43fade6aac0c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1540_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1541_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1543_">No, the Emma Climax® Hybrid is not a medical device.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1544_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1545_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d5b1d943-fade-4aac-8c22-bf1767b3f640" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long can my Emma Climax® Hybrid stay in the box for?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d5b1d943-fade-4aac-8c22-bf1767b3f640" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1547_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1548_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1550_">The Emma Climax® Hybrid shouldn't be left rolled up in the box for more than four weeks after delivery as this may damage your mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1551_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1552_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="ac0c22bf-1767-43f6-8071-17e5912da89a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do I need to flip and ventilate it?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="ac0c22bf-1767-43f6-8071-17e5912da89a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1554_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1555_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1557_">No need for the extra hassle! Flipping your Emma Climax® Hybrid is not necessary and the Ultradry® Pillowtop Cover should always remain on top. The mattress is specially engineered with a specific top to bottom layering to give you zero motion transfer, pressure relief and zoned support for years of comfortable night’s sleep.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1558_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1559_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1560_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1562_">Returns &amp; Delivery</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1563_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1564_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1565_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2da89afa-b8e7-4f99-b0e9-136c1e21b1e9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I return my Emma Climax® Hybrid?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2da89afa-b8e7-4f99-b0e9-136c1e21b1e9" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1567_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1568_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1570_">You may return your Emma Climax® Hybrid within 365 nights of receiving your product. When you want to return your Emma Climax® Hybrid, please contact our Customer Care agents from 6 AM - 9 PM EST through our available channels:
