</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1590_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1591_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1592_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1593_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1595_">Email: support@emma-sleep.ca&nbsp;</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1596_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1598_">Landline: +1-888-585-3662</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1599_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1601_">or speak directly with an agent using our live-chat feature on our website.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-gjNHFA hBngIv pf-1602_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1603_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1604_"><h4 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1605_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1607_">Upholstered Bed Frame&nbsp;</span></h4><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1608_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1610_">About the Upholstered Bed Frame&nbsp;</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1611_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1612_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1613_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="95a0bebb-12b2-448b-a299-6efe914fedaa" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Upholstered Bed Frame non-flammable?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="95a0bebb-12b2-448b-a299-6efe914fedaa" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1615_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1616_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1618_">Yes, it is non-flammable. It has also passed the cigarette test, which means that it does not easily catch on fire.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1619_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1620_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="8be2996e-fe91-4fed-aa11-a49366423c0e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Upholstered Bed Frame vegan?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="8be2996e-fe91-4fed-aa11-a49366423c0e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1622_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1623_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1625_">Yes, the Upholstered Bed Frame is 100 % vegan and does not contain any animal-based materials, nor is tested on animals. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1626_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1627_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="edaa11a4-9366-423c-8ef7-677146d0f2ba" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I buy it without the headboard? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="edaa11a4-9366-423c-8ef7-677146d0f2ba" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1629_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1630_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1632_">Unfortunately, not at the moment. If you decide not to use it, you can always store it. The Upholstered Bed Frame even offers you enough storage space to place it underneath the bed, if you decide not to use it. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1633_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1634_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="3c0ef767-7146-40f2-bab0-eb2429c54f65" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I use an electric slatted frame? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3c0ef767-7146-40f2-bab0-eb2429c54f65" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1636_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1637_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1639_">No. The slats that are delivered with the bed cannot be replaced by an electric slatted frame due to the construction of the bed.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1640_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1641_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="f2bab0eb-2429-454f-a5bd-6cce952f72d2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do you offer different colors?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="f2bab0eb-2429-454f-a5bd-6cce952f72d2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1643_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1644_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1646_">At present, we offer only the color grey for the Upholstered Bed Frame.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1647_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1648_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="4f65bd6c-ce95-4f72-927c-0862df12e47b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How durable is the Upholstered Bed Frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4f65bd6c-ce95-4f72-927c-0862df12e47b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1650_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1651_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1653_">The Upholstered Bed Frame is highly durable and has gone through several durability tests during its development to ensure its quality. It has been tested to be able to withstand up to 500 lbs of force - meaning it can hold up a lot of weight. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1654_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1655_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="72d27c08-62df-42e4-bbf9-a12944d27e53" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I place the Upholstered Bed Frame in the middle of the room?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="72d27c08-62df-42e4-bbf9-a12944d27e53" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1657_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1658_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1660_">Yes, but we recommend placing the Emma Upholstered Bed Frame against a wall. This will offer you the maximum amount of stability for your bed frame. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1661_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1662_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="e47bf9a1-2944-427e-9385-18fb609ef23c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long is the guarantee? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e47bf9a1-2944-427e-9385-18fb609ef23c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1664_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1665_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1667_">We have a 60 night-trial and 5 years warranty on the product (excluding the screws). </span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1668_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1669_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1670_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1672_">Is the Emma Upholstered Bed Frame right for you?&nbsp;</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1673_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1674_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1675_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9ef23c00-59f7-415c-98a5-386bc6790ac6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can the bed be used without a headboard? Can I use my own?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9ef23c00-59f7-415c-98a5-386bc6790ac6" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1677_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1678_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1680_">Yes, the Upholstered Bed Frame may be used without a headboard and you may also use your own headboard. After both boxes have arrived, you can decide whether to use the headboard or not. The Upholstered Bed Frame even offers you enough storage to put it underneath the bed, if you decide not to use it.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1681_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1682_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="5c58a538-6bc6-490a-86ea-446c4565c9ca" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I use my own slats for the bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5c58a538-6bc6-490a-86ea-446c4565c9ca" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1684_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1685_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1687_">Unfortunately, no. The Emma Upholstered Bed Frame has its own suspension that is uniquely designed with FlexiSlats® that help provide additional pressure-relief for your back and joints and an AirFlow® bed base that helps maximize breathability.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1688_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1689_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="0ac6ea44-6c45-45c9-8a2d-8ee55065b2bd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do I need to use the Emma Original mattress with it, or would another mattress be fine as well? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0ac6ea44-6c45-45c9-8a2d-8ee55065b2bd" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1691_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1692_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1694_">You can use the bed with any mattress and any topper. To get the best sleep experience, we would of course recommend using an Emma mattress with your Upholstered Bed Frame. If you want to get the Boxspring bed experience, you can add a topper to it too. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1695_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1696_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c9ca2d8e-e550-45b2-bd65-5f94cc6f292c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How high is the Upholstered Bed frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c9ca2d8e-e550-45b2-bd65-5f94cc6f292c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1698_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1699_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1701_">Our Upholstered bedframe has a maximum height of 43 inches (with the headboard) and a bed height of 14 inches without the mattress and 24 inches with the mattress.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1702_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1703_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="b2bd655f-94cc-4f29-acec-f794de717fe5" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the dimensions of your Bed Frames?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b2bd655f-94cc-4f29-acec-f794de717fe5" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1705_"><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1706_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1707_"><div class="sc-hjGZqJ fbWulc pf-1708_ pf-table-default" data-pf-type="Table"><table><tbody><tr><th class="A1"><span>Size</span></th><th class="B1"><span>Length</span></th><th class="C1"><span>Width</span></th><th class="D1"><span>Height</span></th><th class="E1"><span>Weight</span></th></tr><tr><td class="A2"><span>Full</span></td><td class="B2"><span>75.20 in</span></td><td class="C2"><span>53.94 in</span></td><td class="D2"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E2"><span>121 lbs</span></td></tr><tr><td class="A3"><span>Queen</span></td><td class="B3"><span>79.92 in</span></td><td class="C3"><span>60.24 in</span></td><td class="D3"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E3"><span>129.8 lbs </span></td></tr><tr><td class="A4"><span>King</span></td><td class="B4"><span>79.92 in</span></td><td class="C4"><span>75.98 in</span></td><td class="D4"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E4"><span>158.4 lbs</span></td></tr><tr><td class="A5"><span>California King</span></td><td class="B5"><span>83.86 in</span></td><td class="C5"><span>72.05 in</span></td><td class="D5"><span>43.30 in</span></td><td class="E5"><span>147.4 lbs</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1709_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1710_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1711_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1713_">How do I take care of and assemble my bed frame?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1714_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1715_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1716_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="717fe5c0-39ff-4a04-b472-1676a7442d3b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I assemble my Upholstered Bed Frame?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="717fe5c0-39ff-4a04-b472-1676a7442d3b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1718_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1719_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1721_">Assembling the Upholstered Bed Frame may take 30-45 minutes. We have a manual and a video to guide you on this. Please view the manual for instructions <a href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0562/9873/3706/files/Upholstered_Bedframe_-_Instructions.pdf?v=1658750087" target="_blank">here.</a> For an instructional video, please view <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6GBNFJFQe4Y&amp;ab_channel=EmmaMattress" target="_blank">here.
</a></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1722_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1723_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="04b47216-76a7-442d-bb33-4cf9d451ad54" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long does it take to dismantle it? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="04b47216-76a7-442d-bb33-4cf9d451ad54" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1725_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1726_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1728_">The Upholstered Bed Frame can be dismantled in less than 15 minutes.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1729_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1730_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="2d3b334c-f9d4-41ad-9472-34141ab963c3" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I clean my new Upholstered Bed Frame? </span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="2d3b334c-f9d4-41ad-9472-34141ab963c3" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1732_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1733_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1735_">For small stains, wet a clean cloth with a little bit of soap. For bigger stains, you may use stain removers found in your local store.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1736_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1737_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1738_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1740_">R