"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the certifications of the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3f1bab17-7f93-4a9f-bbf3-e03fbacd4dc1" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1826_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1827_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1829_">The Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow is OEKO-Tex® 100 Certified Class 1 (16.0.93305) of OEKO-Tex Standard 100. This certification suggests a high standard and is even suitable for infants/toddlers up to 3 years old. Check more at their website <a href="https://www.oeko-tex.com/en/our-standards/standard-100-by-oeko-tex" target="_blank">here. 
</a></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1830_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1831_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="9f3bf3e0-3fba-4d4d-81d0-b9ffc14cb851" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What is the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow made of?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="9f3bf3e0-3fba-4d4d-81d0-b9ffc14cb851" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1833_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1834_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1836_">The Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow is made of three adjustable foam layers that provides bespoke comfort for any type of sleeper with a removable Plus UltraDry Cover®. The three layers are:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1837_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1838_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-1839_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1840_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1842_">Supportive Visco Foam that conforms to your head and neck for more support.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1843_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1845_">Cool AIRGOCELL® Foam which is our softest layer that allows for breathability and cooling.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-1846_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1848_">Visco Memory Foam that distributes weight for optimal pressure relief.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1849_"><button