play:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1871_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1872_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1874_">Yes, the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow is vegan. No animals were harmed, used, or tested in the manufacturing of our pillows.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-1875_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-1876_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-1877_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1879_">Is the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-1880_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1881_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1882_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="b18c0ed2-249d-454d-9843-74935ec3303f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How is the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow able to adjust to my sleep?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b18c0ed2-249d-454d-9843-74935ec3303f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1884_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1885_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1887_">The Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow is adjustable for any type of sleeper. The three different layers can be interchanged as you see fit. Its Supportive Visco Foam layer conforms to your head and neck so that your head is cradled and well-supported. Its AIRGOCELL® Foam layer is the softest layer which dissipates sweat and distributes heat for cool and breathable comfort. While its Pressure-relieving Viscose Foam has a slightly softer feel but consistent pressure relief for optimal support.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1888_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1889_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="4d584374-935e-4330-bf37-0e5e2e42d028" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow stay cool at night?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4d584374-935e-4330-bf37-0e5e2e42d028" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1891_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1892_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1894_">Yes it does. The Plush UltraDry® breathable cover has a knit design for optimal airflow and our AIRGOCELL® foam cooling technology dissipates sweat and distributes heat so that you keep a cool and comfortable sleep  throughout the night.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-1895_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-1896_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="303f370e-5e2e-42d0-a8dc-daf2d8482571" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow hypoallergenic?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="303f370e-5e2e-42d0-a8dc-daf2d8482571" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-1898_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-1899_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-1901_">The Emma Original Adjustable Foam Pillow is a breathable and hypoallergenic pillow perfect for sensitive and hot sleepers.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="s