for your comfort in sleep. In simple terms, it reduces the likelihood for allergens to affect you during sleep.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2000_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2001_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="fdd13cdd-e6e5-4306-b584-ecd5ebb33eff" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I put the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector on the mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="fdd13cdd-e6e5-4306-b584-ecd5ebb33eff" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2003_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2004_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2006_">Putting on the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector is quick and easy. It’s adjustable and flexible. You just need to wrap it around your mattress and you’re good to go. For visual instruction, you may view <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FItaOpA7kNM&amp;ab_channel=EmmaMattress" target="_blank">here.
