-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2030_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-2031_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2033_">Is the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-2034_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2035_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2036_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="d0e6a191-ab7a-4ca7-8d32-412b1ac1015a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Why is the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector the perfect addition to my mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d0e6a191-ab7a-4ca7-8d32-412b1ac1015a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2038_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2039_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2041_">With the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector’s Tri-Protect™ Action, it serves as a protective layer for you and your mattress. By preventing unwanted stains and reducing allergens, and ensuring breathability in your mattress, you are able to prolong the life of your Emma Original Mattress while ensuring a safe sleep environment for you and your family.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2042_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2043_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="a74d3241-2b1a-4101-9ac1-01dd6a2112b3" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Will the Breathable Mattress Protector affect my mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="a74d3241-2b1a-4101-9ac1-01dd6a2112b3" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2045_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2046_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2048_">No. The Emma Breathable Mattress Protector is made to complement your Emma Original Mattress. With that, you don’t need to worry about your protector interfering with your mattress benefits.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2049_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2050_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="015ac101-dd6a-4112-b3af-2351fdb1cdb1" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Breathable Mattress Protector sleep hot?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="015ac101-dd6a-4112-b3af-2351fdb1cdb1" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2052_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2053_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2055_">No. The Emma Breathable Mattress protector is made with a breathable material with a woven design that allows for better air circulation so that you can get a cool and comfortable night’s sleep.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2056_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2057_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-2058_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2060_">How do I take care of my Emma Breathable Mattress Protector?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-2061_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2062_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2063_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="b1cdb187-262f-4d37-bcdb-6cc9c321d2ad" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash my Emma Breathable Mattress Protector?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b1cdb187-262f-4d37-bcdb-6cc9c321d2ad" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2065_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2066_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2068_">Yes. For specific information on washing, you may see their individual wash-label details.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2072_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2073_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="6cc9c321-d2ad-45c5-835d-a228be784e4b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How often should I wash my protector?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="6cc9c321-d2ad-45c5-835d-a228be784e4b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2075_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2076_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2078_">We recommend washing it once every 3 months.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2079_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2080_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="c5835da2-28be-484e-8b33-35e3b2265aec" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector waterproof?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="c5835da2-28be-484e-8b33-35e3b2265aec" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2082_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2083_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2085_">Yes, the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector is waterproof. This means that liquid will not get into your Emma Original Mattress as long as the Breathable Mattress Protector is there.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2086_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2087_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="4e4b3335-e3b2-465a-acb0-a5b7a77db23f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector completely stain-resistant?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4e4b3335-e3b2-465a-acb0-a5b7a77db23f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2089_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2090_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2092_">Yes, the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector is completely stain-resistant. Although, colored liquids may still discolor the protective layer (i.e. red wine); however, these stains can still be washed off in the washing machine at a maximum of 40°C.
