67-bbcd25245f5d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2176_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2177_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2179_">We offer toppers for 4 sizes for our Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2180_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2181_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-2182_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2183_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2185_">Twin: 75’’ x 38” x 2” (10 lbs) - Best for children, teens, or anyone under six feet tall.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2186_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2188_">Full: 75” x 54” x 2” (14 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples looking for something compact yet comfortable</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2189_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2191_">Queen: 80” x 56” x 2” (17 lbs) - Best for individuals or couples who want extra space.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2192_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2194_">King: 80” x 76” x 2” (22 lbs) - Best for families who sleep together.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2195_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2196_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="7b5abc16-4762-4a3d-83e4-5894d942040f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>When do I buy the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7b5abc16-4762-4a3d-83e4-5894d942040f" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2198_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2199_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2201_">The Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper is ideal if you want your mattress softness/firmness to change. Our reversible feature allows you to make your mattress feel firmer or softer depending on your preference.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2202_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2203_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="3d83e458-94d9-4204-8f8a-c20babcdd5bb" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What is the cover made of?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3d83e458-94d9-4204-8f8a-c20babcdd5bb" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2205_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2206_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2208_">The Plush UltraDry® Cover of the Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper is made of 99% Polyester and 1% Elastane. It is a knitted white fabric that is completely detachable from the topper through a zipper.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2209_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2210_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-2211_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2213_">Is the Emma Reversible Topper right for you?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-2214_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2215_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2216_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="056e4792-ebb9-470c-b3ff-a2773d924782" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How will the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper affect my mattress?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="056e4792-ebb9-470c-b3ff-a2773d924782" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2218_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2219_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2221_">Adding our Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper will change the softness/firmness of your mattress, depending on the side that you use.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2222_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2223_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="0cf3ffa2-773d-4247-8262-a4e4ad0fa142" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What weight should I be to enjoy the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0cf3ffa2-773d-4247-8262-a4e4ad0fa142" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2225_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2226_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2228_">We recommend the topper to people between 50 kg and 130 kg. </span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2229_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2230_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="478262a4-e4ad-4fa1-82db-c87588256990" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>What are the advantages of the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="478262a4-e4ad-4fa1-82db-c87588256990" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2232_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2233_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2235_">The Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper allows you to control the softness or firmness of your mattress to suit your preference.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2236_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2237_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="a142dbc8-7588-4569-90db-395b38a5ad13" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How thick is the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="a142dbc8-7588-4569-90db-395b38a5ad13" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2239_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2240_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2242_">The Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper is approximately 2 inches thick.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2243_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2244_"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iUKqMP iPshnk pf-2245_ header"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2247_">How do I take care of my Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></h6><div class="sc-iCfMLu dkvyUF pf-2248_ pf-icon-left" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2249_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2250_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="a5ad1382-24b5-4cbd-973c-3750ae78115a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I install my Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="a5ad1382-24b5-4cbd-973c-3750ae78115a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2252_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2253_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2255_">To prevent shifting around the mattress, you should install your Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper underneath your mattress sheets. If you’re using the Emma Breathable Mattress Protector, it should also go under your Protector.<br><br>To sum it up, the order of layers should be:<br></span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2256_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2257_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-2258_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2259_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2261_">Emma Original Mattress</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2262_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2264_">Emma Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2265_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2267_">Emma Breathable Mattress Protector (if applicable)</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2268_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2270_">Mattress Sheets</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2271_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2272_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="3fec939c-527a-42bb-9c38-98a774188143" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper go under my mattress protector and sheets?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3fec939c-527a-42bb-9c38-98a774188143" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-gKclnd dMSgnu pf-2274_"><p class="sc-eFegNN jgBUGG pf-2275_ header" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2277_">&nbsp;You should install your Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper underneath both the mattress protector and sheets. The sum it up, the order of layers should be:</span></p><div class="sc-llYSUQ bhKSKZ pf-2278_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eGPXGI dIjtdz pf-2279_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:1px" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-fXEqDS fVXmAe pf-2280_"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2281_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2283_">Emma Original Mattress</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2284_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2286_">Emma Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2287_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2289_">Emma Breathable Mattress Protector (if applicable)</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-FNXRL brLfuZ pf-2290_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmciRz hKEAti pf-2292_">Mattress Sheets</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-2293_"><button type="button" class="sc-jRQBWg fpohrn pf-2294_ custom-font pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="367c259a-9c38-4bdf-8b9f-cee52bbe8870" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I wash the Emma Firm-to-Soft Reversible Topper?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="367c259a-9c38-4bdf-8b9f-cee52bbe8870" sty